{"tid":877953,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"MSI Gaming Notebook求評","createTime":"2018-10-26T17:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T06:03:48.000Z","uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b6aed3edfeb52673bd9c99d10c507d284169c7d5","tid":877953,"uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:43:53.000Z","msg":"小弟睇中左呢部新出左無耐既GE75 Raider<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msi.com/Laptop/GE75-Raider-8RX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msi.com%2FLaptop%2FGE75-Raider-8RX&d=it6KRJNEdhxNhCOcXRRuuCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=637e237a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.msi.com/Laptop/GE75-Raider-8RX</a><br />\n<br />\nSPEC:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msi.com/Laptop/GE75-Raider-8RX/Specification\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msi.com%2FLaptop%2FGE75-Raider-8RX%2FSpecification&d=it6KRJNEdhxNhCOcXRRuuCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=db3a3f19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.msi.com/Laptop/GE75-Raider-8RX/Specification</a><br />\n<br />\n諗住買顯示卡1070版<br />\n<br />\n用途:主要for食雞 打魔獸爭霸3  得閒可能直播下自己打機比圍內識既朋友睇<br />\n<br />\n同埋自己讀Media科 平時都應該會拎番學校用<br />\n<br />\n未來要剪片 要畫野 用Premiere 用Adobe Illustrator&lrm;<br />\n<br />\n部機本身16GB RAM 想問下我升32GB RAM for 剪片 畫野 直播 作用大唔大?<br />\n<br />\n同埋想換隻1TB SSD入去 諗住部機長用 Down好多game玩<br />\n<br />\nHDD都可能加小小<br />\n<br />\n門市好似做緊$16900左右<br />\n<br />\n加埋SSD 同 RAM 應該2萬左右"},{"pid":"9c2cfb5f4397da1395f37ffc759d51797dd11bda","tid":877953,"uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/27/dQ1MHv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2FdQ1MHv.png&h=8b04901a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/27/q9F1Pz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2Fq9F1Pz.png&h=77a94865&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0332306427ed51a9bacd882fd8d5fc6c78eda99","tid":877953,"uid":199262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T19:26:24.000Z","msg":"畢值咁高不如買部輕身上堂用laptop加部desktop好過 laptop幾貴都好 有咁上下性能的話散熱同便攜性都好難做得好  你仲要多工<br />\n斷估直播係坐定定打機唔係邊行邊打掛"},{"pid":"dd28d9478b6f106042989e7c26387e37c4479557","tid":877953,"uid":139538,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T19:44:25.000Z","msg":"直播/穩定買desktop<br />\n<br />\nlaptop易過熱降頻"},{"pid":"e1319b8fdb70932ff8b12bc9ba27862cd4f8d0c1","tid":877953,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T20:32:40.000Z","msg":"練臂力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c9df76955463b961c0e4573cd1009ef79d62d9","tid":877953,"uid":35560,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T20:42:53.000Z","msg":"咪撚買微星<br />\n本人一路支持左微星好多年 好多野都用佢<br />\n但岩岩老婆部notebook個轉軸位爆左<br />\n上網睇過原來好多人都係咁<br />\n睇網上d人講話拎去維修部整既話會比佢話係人為整爆要自己比錢先有得整<br />\n屌啦媽我老婆部notebook成萬8蚊都可以咁撚化學<br />\n聽日就拎部notebook上漢科睇佢講乜<br />\n真係諗起都嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/044240_1ea5b0fcdf1d5c0d6aee96b17d6b4442.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F044240_1ea5b0fcdf1d5c0d6aee96b17d6b4442.jpg&h=98e2f522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/044242_c11d2037284140126cece52e28d01180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F044242_c11d2037284140126cece52e28d01180.jpg&h=7ec4bd4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/044245_28651abaa7610f3e7f64f2e53ec0c1b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F044245_28651abaa7610f3e7f64f2e53ec0c1b4.jpg&h=d40bbb9d&s={SIZE}